title: azfamily
description:
Get breaking news alerts, weather updates and live video delivered straight to your smart phone, 24/7.
Plus:
- Forecasts from Arizona’s Weather Authority
- Good Morning Arizona feature stories
- CBS 5 Investigative reports
- 3 On Your Side consumer news
- Dirty Dining reports
- Live streaming video of 3TV & CBS 5 newscasts
- A direct connection to the 3TV & CBS 5 news desk for your story ideas and news tips.
Download the azfamily news app today and stay connected!
